<img src="peaches.jpg">
<h2>Summery feast for a Winter's Day</h2>
<h1>Fiesta Peach Spam Bake</h1>
<p>
  <span>Drain</span> 825 mL canned sliced peaches, reserving the syrup.
</p>
<p>
  <span>Slice</span> whole Spam into 5 sections, but not all the way through, so that's still all one piece.
</p>
<p>
  <span>Insert</span> peach slices between the Spam slices. Arrange remaining slices around the Spam.
</p>
<p>
  <span>Blend</span> a quarter of a cup of the reserved syrup with 2 tbsp of brown sugar, and pour over the Spam.
</p>
<p>
  <span>Stud</span> the Spam with cloves.
</p>
<p>
  <span>Bake</span> at 190Â°C for about 35 minutes.
</p>
